summary: Experienced HR Director with over 10 years of HR experience across multiple facilities, including employee relations, benefits administration, 401(k) management, payroll, EEOC, AAP, FAA/DOT compliance, workers' compensation and safety.

experience.title: HR Director
experience.description: Oversees onboarding, hiring and recruiting; administers benefits (health, dental, vision, life, disability); 401(k) administration; payroll management including garnishments; timekeeping system updates; FMLA administration; unemployment and workers' compensation coordination; HR & safety orientation; I-9 & E-Verify administration; COBRA/5500 filings; training system management; annual reviews and personnel actions; disciplinary actions and terminations; temporary help management; HR communications; safety and OSHA recordkeeping; EEOC/AAP compliance; liaises with safety director; maintains confidential employee records.
